es, IOBC provides strategic support and funding to innovative startups. The firm is dedicated to fostering breakthroughs in cutting-edge fields, leveraging its expertise and network to drive success and growth for its portfolio companies.</div>\n</div>","tier":"Gold","location":"","categories":["VC/Finance"]}}]}]]}]}]],null,null],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4","children":["$","$L16",null,{"target":"/partners","text":"View All Sponsors"}]}]]}]]}]
b:["$","div",null,{"className":"w-full text-left mt-2 mb-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-row items-center justify-between","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-color1 w-10 h-1 mt-2"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mt-2 text-color5","children":"Exhibitiors"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"hidden md:block","children":["$","button",null,{"data-tally-layout":"modal","data-tally-open":"nPl9xe","data-tally-width":"700","data-tally-emoji-text":"👋","data-tally-emoji-animation":"wave","data-tally-auto-close":"3000","className":"bg-color1 hover:bg-color2 text-color7 py-2 px-4 font-bold rounded ease-in-out duration-300","onClick":"$undefined","children":"Become Our Exhibitor"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-1 text-color2","children":"MEET OUR EXHIBITIORS"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-col mt-4 items-center justify-center gap-y-4 w-full h-full","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-y-4 gap-x-4","children":[["$","div","353340",{"className":"w-full h-36 md:w-[23%] md:h-27 md:min-w-48 md:min-h-27","children":["$","$L15",null,{"type":"exhibitor","organization":{"id":353340,"name":"1Gen AI","url":"https://www.1gen.ai/","logo":"https://d1keuthy5s86c8.cloudfront.net/genai_202405/ab0ff9c4d49cf9bb1596f7dbe8a0c07ca690cc6486dd9b1966b472daf69e5b3a_1/1gen.png","desc":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Meet 1Gen, the Anime AI marketing and sales tools for community.<br>1Gen bot is a #GENAI assistant in the vein of AI Copilot, a next-level bot assistant. 1Gen can take on and finish an entire sale project on its own. To put it to work, you give it a job&mdash;&ldquo;Acquire traffic that maps all the potential buyers in a telegram group,&rdquo;&mdash;and the AI performs an intention based engagement (conversation, meme, and photos) to find the targets, gets their attention and contact information, then builds and finishes a transaction or an engagement. 1Gen builds all above on top of its in-house multimodal LLM for entertaining and gaming industries.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Follow our twitter for <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/1genai\">more</a></span>.</p>","tier":"Type A","location":"","categories":["GenAI App"]}}]}],["$","div","353431",{"className":"w-full h-36 md:w-[23%] md:h-27 md:min-w-48 md:min-h-27","children":["$","$L15",null,{"type":"exhibitor","organization":{"id":353431,"name":"FinalizeAI","url":"https://dev.finalize.ai/","logo":"https://d1keuthy5s86c8.cloudfront.net/genai_202405/7cf63bdba96588b076da4a8eb75ef810fece21dc121c54056256da0eb55f604a_1/finalize.png","desc":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Diverse AI Products: Explore a wide range of AI tools designed for various industries, including office, audio, video, pictures, games, and more. Our solutions are tailored to enhance your projects and drive success.</p>","tier":"Type A","location":"","categories":["GenAI App"]}}]}],["$","div","350756",{"className":"w-full h-36 md:w-[23%] md:h-27 md:min-w-48 md:min-h-27","children":["$","$L15",null,{"type":"exhibitor","organization":{"id":350756,"name":"IOBC Capital","url":"https://www.iobc.capital/","logo":"https://d1keuthy5s86c8.cloudfront.net/genai_202405/4cb675f069f848a5eb87e8143d2dfcdd1c02eeada36e214651a508dd22194cad_1/cropped_img_genai_202405_1715022847045.png","desc":"<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center md:px-3 md:py-2 p-1\">\n<div class=\"mt-4 text-left text-lg md:text-xl\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"mt-4 text-left text-lg md:text-xl\">IOBC is a venture capital firm specializing in investments across the technology and biotechnology sectors. With a focus on early to growth-stage companies, IOBC provides strategic support and funding to innovative startups. The firm is dedicated to fostering breakthroughs in cutting-edge fields, leveraging its expertise and network to drive success and growth for its portfolio companies.</div>\n</div>","tier":"Gold","location":"","categories":["VC/Finance"]}}]}],["$","div","352657",{"className":"w-full h-36 md:w-[23%] md:h-27 md:min-w-48 md:min-h-27","children":["$","$L15",null,{"type":"exhibitor","organization":{"id":352657,"name":"MountainLion AI","url":"https://www.mlion.ai/#/","logo":"https://d1keuthy5s86c8.cloudfront.net/genai_202405/c8c446f7ec0bb8ac14fbb2a6b0bf1c2c970a000482869c898325414752cb4a6b_1/mountainlion.765e6199.png","desc":"<p>Mlion.ai stands at the forefront of the Web3 industry, offering unparalleled expertise and insights into the dynamic world of blockchain and cryptocurrency. As a powerful AIGC (Artificial Intelligence-Generated Content) application, Mlion.ai has meticulously gathered years of data across various dimensions, including industry news, coin price trends, and asset flows. This vast reservoir of knowledge empowers Mlion.ai to provide users with real-time updates and a deep understanding of the ever-evolving market landscape.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Follower our Twitter <a href=\"https://x.com/MLion_AI\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">here</span></a>!</p>","tier":"Type A","location":"","categories":["Tech","GenAI App"]}}]}],["$","div","353410",{"className":"w-full h-36 md:w-[23%] md:h-27 md:min-w-48 md:min-h-27","children":["$","$L15",null,{"type":"exhibitor","organization":{"id":353410,"name":"Puffer Finance","url":"https://www.puffer.fi/#","logo":"https://d1keuthy5s86c8.cloudfront.net/genai_202405/3dfe4eb1f24f723e0a1e120afa59e48f2ce2a22a84b4c3a01a6f05b6478a0652_1/puffer.png","desc":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Puffer is a decentralized native liquid restaking protocol (nLRP) built on Eigenlayer.</p>\n<p>It makes&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.puffer.fi/protocol/puffer-modules/#native-restaking-\">native restaking</a>&nbsp;on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.eigenlayer.xyz/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Eigenlayer</a> more accessible, allowing anyone to run an Ethereum Proof of Stake (PoS) validator while supercharging their rewards.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Follow our Twitter <a href=\"https://x.com/puffer_finance\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">here</span></a>!&nbsp;</p>","tier":"Type A","location":"","categories":["VC/Finance"]}}]}],["$","div","353400",{"className":"w-full h-36 md:w-[23%] md:h-27 md:min-w-48 md:min-h-27","children":["$","$L15",null,{"type":"exhibitor","organization":{"id":353400,"name":"Revia","url":"https://revia.tech/","logo":"https://d1keuthy5s86c8.cloudfront.net/genai_202405/85214a7ccd7effb0ac38b1dc3795964ed76fd11bab631c10b664edcfb5dc9ae7_1/revia.png","desc":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Revia can represent you in phone calls (like tedious calls to customer support). Just give it an objective and some basic information &mdash; and it can handle your calls on autopilot.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Follow our twitter <a href=\"https://x.com/revia_tech\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">here</span></a>!&nbsp;</p>","tier":"Type B","location":"","categories":["GenAI App"]}}]}],["$","div","353342",{"className":"w-full h-36 md:w-[23%] md:h-27 md:min-w-48 md:min-h-27","children":["$","$L15",null,{"type":"exhibitor","organization":{"id":353342,"name":"StarloomAI","url":"https://starloom.ai/#/","logo":"https://d1keuthy5s86c8.cloudfront.net/genai_202405/796da0237d1196346a4034166133973cf53744259dff596998bb5cd28b1eb738_1/85878b0bd63c9001c7d3c896ba3a081.png","desc":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Many people are interested in metaphysics, feng shui, and fortune-telling. However, there are many imposters among the true masters. For entrepreneurs and the wealthy, a single reading from a genuine master can be worth a fortune.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Try Starloom, where top masters offer free fortune-telling! Our AI metaphysics master, trained with nearly ten thousand enlightened data points and guided by a team of professional feng shui masters, combines the wisdom of 5-10 top experts. Experience top-tier fortune-telling guidance without leaving your home.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Try <a href=\"https://starloom.ai\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Starloom</span></a> for free now!</p>","tier":"Type A","location":"","categories":["GenAI App"]}}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4","children":["$","$L16",null,{"target":"/exhibitors","text":"View All Exhibitors"}]}]]}]]}]
